  "texts": [
    "For all the training, we use SGD optimizer with momentum 0.9 and cosine learning rate annealing.",
    "Weight decay is set to 1×10 -4, and 1 × 10 -5 for CIFAR-10 and CIFAR-100, respectively.",
    "Particularly, for our proposed ANL methods, weight decay is set to 0 for all datasets.",
    "The initial learning rate is set to 0.01 for CIFAR-10 and 0.1 for CIFAR-100.",
    "Batch size is set to 128."
  ],
